FBIS3-60848 "jptot001__l94096" JPRS-TOT-94-001-L Document Type:JPRS Document Title:Terrorism FOUO 7 January 1994 CENTRAL EURASIA RUSSIA Four Caucasians Kidnap Children; No Motive Given Helicopter Arrives in Mineralnyye Vody LD2412043493 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 0352 GMT 24 Dec 93 LD2412043493 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service Language: Russian Article Type:BFN [Excerpt] After a 90-minute flight from Krasnodar, the helicopter, still under the control of the group of armed bandits and with the group of schoolchildren taken hostage in Rostov, arrived at Mineralnyye Vody airport. An ITAR-TASS correspondent was told by responsible employees at the operational headquarters, who are continuing talks with the bandits, that none of the children has been hurt and exhaustive measures are being taken to save them. [passage omitted]
